FUNC 关闭软件
    FOR
        IF @防止SWITCH休眠 > 95
            FOR 3
                B
                50
            NEXT
        ELSE
            HOME DOWN
            100
            HOME UP
            1000
            X
            WAIT 1000
            A
            WAIT 1500
            A
            WAIT 1000
            A
            BREAK
        ENDIF
    NEXT
ENDFUNC
